{"tha-ap343:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap343:0.2":"Ekapadumiyavagga ","tha-ap343:0.3":"Ekapadumiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap343:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap343:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap343:1.3":"Bhavabhave vibhavento, ","tha-ap343:1.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap343:2.1":"Hamsaraja tada homi, ","tha-ap343:2.2":"dijanam pavaro aham; ","tha-ap343:2.3":"Jatassaram samogayha, ","tha-ap343:2.4":"kilami hamsakilitam. ","tha-ap343:3.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap343:3.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap343:3.3":"Jatassarassa upari, ","tha-ap343:3.4":"agacchi tavade jino. ","tha-ap343:4.1":"Disvanaham devadevam, ","tha-ap343:4.2":"sayambhum lokanayakam; ","tha-ap343:4.3":"Vante chetvana padumam, ","tha-ap343:4.4":"satapattam manoramam. ","tha-ap343:5.1":"Mukhatundena paggayha, ","tha-ap343:5.2":"pasanno lokanayake; ","tha-ap343:5.3":"Ukkhipitvana gagane, ","tha-ap343:5.4":"buddhasettham apujayim. ","tha-ap343:6.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap343:6.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap343:6.3":"Antalikkhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap343:6.4":"aka me anumodanam. ","tha-ap343:7.1":"‘Imina ekapadumena, ","tha-ap343:7.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap343:7.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap343:7.4":"vinipatam na gacchasi’. ","tha-ap343:8.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap343:8.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap343:8.3":"Mama kammam pakittetva, ","tha-ap343:8.4":"agama yena patthitam. ","tha-ap343:9.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap343:9.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap343:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap343:9.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap343:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap343:10.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap343:10.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap343:10.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap343:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekapadumiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap343:12.1":"Ekapadumiyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}